Package: DGEobj.plots
Type:    Package
Title:   Differential Gene Expression (DGE) Analysis Plots
Version: 1.0.0.9000
Description: 
    Provides a function toolkit to facilitate reproducible RNA-Seq DGE
    analysis by standardizing several types of common plots. The DGE Plotting tools
    are suitable for downstream analysis visualizations and include: profilePlot,
    volcanoPlot, comparePlot, plotPvalHist, ggplotMDS, and others.
